This is the main entry point that other plugins use. It provides two modes of operation:

| Method | Mode | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `getGatekeeperValue()` | **JIT (recommended)** | Suspend function. Uses batched, on-demand fetching via `JitGatekeeperService`. Ensures proper exposure attribution. |
