| `refreshAndIsGkEnabled()` | Legacy + force refresh | Forces a sync before returning the value. |
| `getAllGkValues()` | Debugging | Merges values from both eager and JIT caches. |
| `refreshAndGetAllGkValues()` | Debugging | Refreshes the eager cache and returns all values. |

